data.description: Fabulous Atoka 5BR/3BA home, some TLC needed -  Spacious Great Room w/FP; Kitchen has granite, new appliances, lots of storage & large dining area; amazing sunroom-great for a home office or 2nd living space; split floorplan down; primary bed w/attached bath w/2 closets; upstairs: 2 more beds + bath (there is a closet big enough to be another bed); 20x30 shed w/power in a fenced backyard. New flooring; downstairs HVAC recently replaced. Lot extends to the neighbors fence on left so much space!
